nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: An orbital ring encircles Earth, its gleaming metal surface dotted with docking stations and habitat modules. Space elevators stretch from equatorial points, their carbon nanotube cables shimmering. Photorealistic render with Earth's curvature visible.

The galaxy's largest shipyard, spanning the orbit of a gas giant and its moons. Massive skeletal structures of half-built capital ships float in the void, swarmed by countless construction drones that weave hull plates and conduits like metallic spiders. The gas giant's rings have been mined into a sparse halo, fueling the endless production. At the center of this industrial web, a city-sized station pulsates with energy, coordinating the monumental effort to build a fleet capable of intergalactic travel.
